WEBVTT

00:01:29.256 --> 00:01:31.391
as I know it is so many of yours.

00:01:33.848 --> 00:01:36.787
You may be happy to know
that your research will pay off.

00:01:38.160 --> 00:01:40.398
I am 318 years old.

00:01:41.486 --> 00:01:45.257
The average human lifespan
is now 432 years,

00:01:45.281 --> 00:01:48.561
and my work has been to extend
the human lifespan indefinitely.

00:01:49.363 --> 00:01:51.850
And I've never questioned that someday,

00:01:51.874 --> 00:01:54.816
we'll reach a point
where we'll be content.

00:01:56.959 --> 00:01:58.565
But the opposite keeps happening:

00:01:58.589 --> 00:02:01.063
the longer we live,
the longer we want to live,